This paper is about natural language understanding and sentence representation using neural networks, which falls under the category of computational linguistics (cs.CL). The paper also discusses the use of attention mechanisms and gated recurrent units, which are common techniques in machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The paper also mentions the use of neural networks for classification tasks, which is a common topic in neural networks (cs.NE) and computer vision (cs.CV).
